vta.core

Load

Related Doc: package core

class Load extends Module

Load.

Load inputs and weights from memory (DRAM) into scratchpads (SRAMs). This module instantiate the TensorLoad unit which is in charge of loading 1D and 2D tensors to scratchpads, so it can be used by other modules such as Compute.
